WEBVTT

00:07:59.840 --> 00:08:03.360
It's going to be ideology
or the chase for a profit.

00:08:04.120 --> 00:08:06.680
And they're going to go
for designer babies.

00:08:08.240 --> 00:08:12.096
So why should we be concerned about this?

00:08:12.120 --> 00:08:15.336
We know from Darwin,
if we go back two centuries,

00:08:15.360 --> 00:08:19.496
that evolution and genetics
profoundly have impacted humanity,

00:08:19.520 --> 00:08:21.656
who we are today.

00:08:21.680 --> 00:08:25.616
And some think there's like
a social Darwinism at work in our world,

00:08:25.640 --> 00:08:28.120
and maybe even a eugenics as well.

00:08:28.720 --> 00:08:32.456
Imagine those trends, those forces,